text: Oberurnen was a municipality of the canton of Glarus in Switzerland. On 1 January 2011, the former municipalities of Oberurnen, Bilten, Filzbach, Mollis, Mühlehorn, Näfels, Niederurnen and Obstalden merged into the new municipality of Glarus Nord. ==Other websites== *Website of Oberurnen Category:Former municipalities of Glarus Category:2011 disestablishments in Switzerland
